TS.raw_templates['prefs_notifications'] = "<div id=\"prefs_notifications\" class=\"section_rollup\">\n\n\t<h2 class=\"section_rollup_header\"><ts-icon class=\"ts_icon_bell_o candy_red small_right_margin\"><\/ts-icon>Notification Settings<\/h2>\n\t<p class=\"section_rollup_summary\"><\/p>\n\t<div class=\"section_rollup_details\">\n\n\t\t<div class=\"growls_stuff\" id=\"growls_permission_div\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"desktop_notifications_title\">Desktop Notifications are currently disabled<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p>We strongly recommend enabling notifications so that you'll know when important activity happens on your Slack team.<\/p>\n\t\t\t<p><a class=\"btn btn_success\" id=\"growls_permission_link\"><ts-icon class=\"ts_icon_bell ts_icon_inherit small_right_margin\"><\/ts-icon>Enable desktop notifications<\/a><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"growls_stuff\" id=\"growls_instructions_div\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"desktop_notifications_title\">Desktop Notifications<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"alert alert_info\"><i class=\"ts_icon ts_icon_info_circle\"><\/i>Click <strong>Allow<\/strong> in your browser's pop-up to enable notifications.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"growls_stuff\" id=\"growls_disallowed_div\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"desktop_notifications_title\">Desktop Notifications are currently disabled<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"alert alert_warning\"><i class=\"ts_icon ts_icon_warning\"><\/i>You've disallowed notifications in your browser. You'll need to open your browser preferences to change that.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"growls_stuff\" id=\"growls_impossible_div\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"desktop_notifications_title\">Desktop Notifications are currently disabled<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p><ts-icon class=\"ts_icon_exclamation_triangle\"><\/ts-icon>Your browser does not support desktop notifications. <a href=\"\/downloads\" target=\"_blank\">Try one of our apps<\/a><\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"growls_stuff\" id=\"growls_allowed_div\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"desktop_notifications_title inline_block\" id=\"prefs_send_notifications_for\">Send notifications for:<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"radio\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"notifications_rd\" type=\"radio\" value=\"all\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_send_notifications_for\">\n\t\t\t\t\tAll activity\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"radio\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"notifications_rd\" type=\"radio\" value=\"mentions\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_send_notifications_for\">\n\t\t\t\t\tOnly direct messages and highlight words <span class=\"normal subtle_silver left_margin\">Recommended<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"radio\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"notifications_rd\" type=\"radio\" value=\"never\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_send_notifications_for\">\n\t\t\t\t\tNothing <span class=\"normal subtle_silver left_margin\">Desktop notifications off<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t<p id=\"no_non_default\" class=\"subtle_silver\">You can override your desktop notification preference on a channel-by-channel basis by selecting <em>Channel notification preferences<\/em> in the channel menu. Or, <a href=\"\/account\/notifications\" target=\"{{newWindowName}}\">set preferences for email and mobile notifications<\/a>.<\/p>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"non_default subtle_silver\">Some of your channels have <strong id=\"non_default_tip_link\" class=\"cursor_pointer\">different notification settings<\/strong>. You can also <a href=\"\/account\/notifications\" target=\"{{newWindowName}}\">set preferences for email and mobile notifications<\/a>.<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t<h4 class=\"large_top_margin inline_block\" id=\"prefs_sounds\">Sounds<\/h4>\n\t\t<p class=\"clearfix\">\n\t\t\t{{#foreach notification_sounds}}\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"radio sound_option\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"sound_option_rd\" type=\"radio\" value=\"{{value.value}}\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_sounds\">\n\t\t\t\t\t{{value.label}}\n\t\t\t\t\t{{#if_not_equal value.value compare=\"none\"}}<ts-icon class=\"ts_icon_volume_up ts_icon_inherit\"><\/ts-icon>{{\/if_not_equal}}\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t{{\/foreach}}\n\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t<label class=\"checkbox\">\n\t\t\t\t<input id=\"mute_sounds_cb\" checked=\"checked\" type=\"checkbox\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_mute_all_sounds_label\">\n\t\t\t\t<span id=\"prefs_mute_all_sounds_label\">Mute all sounds<\/span><br>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"normal subtle_silver\">Includes system alerts and notifications for messages<\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t<\/p>\n\n\t\t<h4 class=\"large_top_margin\">Notification Display<\/h4>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t<label class=\"checkbox\">\n\t\t\t\t<input id=\"no_text_in_notifications_cb\" checked=\"checked\" type=\"checkbox\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_show_message_text_label\">\n\t\t\t\t<span id=\"prefs_show_message_text_label\">Show message text in notifications<\/span><br>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"normal subtle_silver\">Uncheck for additional privacy<\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t<\/p>\n\n\t\t{{#if show_mac_ssb_prefs}}\n\t\t\t<h4 id=\"prefs_dock_icon\" class=\"large_top_margin inline_block\">Dock App Icon<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"checkbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input id=\"mac_ssb_bullet_cb\" checked=\"checked\" type=\"checkbox\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_dock_icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\tShow <img src=\"{{versioned_mac_dock_badge}}\" class=\"prefs_mac_dock_badge\"> symbol on icon to indicate unread activity\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"checkbox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input id=\"mac_ssb_bounce_cb\" checked=\"checked\" type=\"checkbox\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_dock_icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\tBounce dock icon when showing a notification\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"checkbox large_left_margin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input id=\"mac_ssb_bounce_short_cb\" checked=\"checked\" type=\"checkbox\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_dock_icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\tBounce it just once\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t{{\/if}}\n\n\t\t{{#if show_win_ssb_prefs}}\n\t\t\t<h4 id=\"winssb_notify_prefs_heading\" class=\"large_top_margin small_bottom_margin inline_block\">App Notification Settings<\/h4>\n\t\t\t<p id=\"winssb_flash_window_heading\" class=\"small_bottom_margin\">Flash window when a notification is received<\/p>\n\t\t\t<p id=\"winssb_flash_window_choices\">\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"radio\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"winssb_flash_window_rd\" type=\"radio\" value=\"never\" data-inline-saver=\"#winssb_notify_prefs_heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\tNever\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"radio\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"winssb_flash_window_rd\" type=\"radio\" value=\"idle\" data-inline-saver=\"#winssb_notify_prefs_heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\tWhen left idle <span class='normal'>(inactive for at least 10 seconds)<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"radio\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<input name=\"winssb_flash_window_rd\" type=\"radio\" value=\"always\" data-inline-saver=\"#winssb_notify_prefs_heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\tAlways\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t<\/p>\n\n\t\t\t<p id=\"winssb_notify_position\">\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"select small col span_1_of_2 no_right_padding\">\n\t\t\t\t\tDisplay notifications on the \n\t\t\t\t\t<select id=\"winssb_notify_corner\" class=\"small\" data-inline-saver=\"#winssb_notify_prefs_heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<option value=\"bottom_right\">bottom-right<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<option value=\"top_right\">top-right<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<option value=\"top_left\">top-left<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<option value=\"bottom_left\">bottom-left<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/select>\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t\t<label class=\"select small col span_1_of_2 no_right_padding\" data-inline-saver=\"#winssb_notify_prefs_heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\tcorner of the\n\t\t\t\t\t<select id=\"winssb_notify_display\" class=\"small\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<option value=\"same_as_app\">same display as app<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<option value=\"primary\">primary display<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/select>\n\t\t\t\t<\/label>\n\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t{{\/if}}\n\n\t\t<p><button id=\"growls_test\" class=\"btn btn_outline\"><i class=\"ts_icon ts_icon_bell_o\"><\/i> Send test notification<\/button><\/p>\n\n\t\t<h4 id=\"prefs_highlight_words\" class=\"large_top_margin inline_block\">Highlight Words<\/h4>\n\t\t<label class=\"normal\">\n\t\t\tTo be notified when someone mentions a word or phrase, add it here. You can separate words or phrases with commas. Highlight words are not case sensitive.\n\t\t\t<input id=\"highlight_words_input\" type=\"text\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_highlight_words\" class=\"small full_width small_top_margin\" {{#feature flag=\"feature_name_tagging_client\"}}{{else}}placeholder='{{#if team_prefs.require_at_for_mention}}Include \"{{member.name}}\" to be notified when you are mentioned without the @{{else}}Your screen name \"{{member.name}}\" is automatically a Highlight Word{{\/if}}'{{\/feature}} value=\"{{highlight_words}}\">\n\t\t<\/label>\n\n\t<\/div>\t\t\n<\/div>\n\n<div id=\"prefs_dnd\" class=\"section_rollup {{#unless has_tz}}tz_not_set{{\/unless}}\">\n\n\t<h2 class=\"do_not_disturb_header section_rollup_header\"><ts-icon class=\"ts_icon_snooze_outline clear_blue small_right_margin\"><\/ts-icon>Do Not Disturb<\/h2>\n\t<p class=\"section_rollup_summary\"><\/p>\n\n\t<div class=\"section_rollup_details\">\n\t\t\n\t\t<p>When Do Not Disturb is activated, Slack won't send desktop, mobile, or email notifications. You can manually snooze notifications by clicking the <i class=\"ts_icon ts_icon_bell_o ts_icon_inherit\"><\/i> icon by your name.<\/p>\n\n\t\t{{#unless has_tz}}\n\t\t\t<p class=\"alert alert_warning missing_tz_alert\">\n\t\t\t\t<i class=\"ts_icon ts_icon_warning\"><\/i>It looks like we've never confirmed your time zone before. We need to do that before turning on Do Not Disturb.\n\t\t\t\t{{#if tz_guess}}\n\t\t\t\t\tIs this correct?\n\t\t\t\t\t<br><strong>{{tz_guess}}<\/strong>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t<button id=\"confirm_dnd_tz_guess\" class=\"btn btn_small small_right_margin\">Yes<\/button>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href='\/account\/settings#timezone' target={{newWindowName}}>Choose a different time zone<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t{{else}}\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href='\/account\/settings#timezone' target={{newWindowName}}>Set your timezone<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t{{\/if}}\n\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t{{\/unless}}\n\n\t\t<label class=\"checkbox hide_if_no_tz\"> \n\t\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"dnd_enabled\" value=\"1\" id=\"dnd_enabled\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_dnd_checkbox_label\">\n\t\t\t<span id=\"prefs_dnd_checkbox_label\">Automatically disable notifications from:<\/span>\n\t\t<\/label>\n\n\t\t<label class=\"select small inline_block no_bottom_margin hide_if_no_tz\">\n\t\t\t<select name=\"dnd_start_hour\" id=\"dnd_start_hour\" class=\"small auto_width\" data-inline-saver=\"#prefs_dnd_checkbox_label\">\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"00:00\">{{#if time24}}00:00{{else}}12:00 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"00:30\">{{#if time24}}00:30{{else}}12:30 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"01:00\">{{#if time24}}01:00{{else}}1:00 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"01:30\">{{#if time24}}01:30{{else}}1:30 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"02:00\">{{#if time24}}02:00{{else}}2:00 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"02:30\">{{#if time24}}02:30{{else}}2:30 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"03:00\">{{#if time24}}03:00{{else}}3:00 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"03:30\">{{#if time24}}03:30{{else}}3:30 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"04:00\">{{#if time24}}04:00{{else}}4:00 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"04:30\">{{#if time24}}04:30{{else}}4:30 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"05:00\">{{#if time24}}05:00{{else}}5:00 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"05:30\">{{#if time24}}05:30{{else}}5:30 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"06:00\">{{#if time24}}06:00{{else}}6:00 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"06:30\">{{#if time24}}06:30{{else}}6:30 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n\t\t\t\t<option value=\"07:00\">{{#if time24}}07:00{{else}}7:00 AM{{\/if}}<\/option>\n